      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MRS. TIGGYWINKLE (1) has some solid form under her belt and proved too classy last time to win by 2.25 lengths at Bendigo in a handy 24.29 beating Love You. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Looks the testing material. SPACE INVADER (6) failed to feature last start after drifting back at this track, but prior to that won by 2 lengths at this track (22.75) beating Paw Quintessa in a Restricted WIN on May 12. Bold showing expected. HOT SUMMER SKY (2) produced a moderate effort last time when seventh at Ballarat over 390m behind Major Wait (23.16) in a Grade 5 H NP. Was a winner prior to that. The form out of her last race has been franked. Key runner on best form. ARCHIE'S GIFT (4) has claims fresh from a recent placing.",
